      "problemId": "prob:airl-operational",
      "problemStatement": "AI and Data Managers struggle with manual, spreadsheet-based readiness assessments when evaluating team and domain AI maturity, resulting in 40+ hours per assessment cycle, inconsistent scoring across teams, and inability to track maturity progression over time.",
      "problemType": "Economic",
